  "title": "Technical Assistant",
  "description": "<p>The Technical Assistance (Newbuilding) supports the\nNewbuilding Department in technical, administrative, and project coordination tasks related to vessel construction, design review, and delivery preparation.<br /><br />·      Ensure PIL Health, Safety, Environment policy is implemented </p><p>·      Propose a continuous improvement plan which will be reported and reviewed on a periodical basis</p><p>·       Technical and Engineering Support</p><p>·       Assist in reviewing structural drawings, plans, and documents from shipyards, equipment makers</p><p>·       Project Coordination</p><p>·       Monitor newbuilding project schedules, milestones, document submissions, and action items.</p><p>·       Coordinate with shipyards, Class, Flag, and internal departments.</p><p>·       Follow up on specification deviations, work progress and drawing approval for the project</p><p>·       And any ad-hoc requirements </p>",
